"Clara" "Will there be extra activity funding?"

"Eve" "No.{change:Eve,smile}"

"Clara" "Vice president, see our guest out."

"Me" "You switched sides way too fast."

"" "Eve walked to the door and gripped the handle."
"" "She glanced back at us."
"" "The door opened, and the sounds of the hallway rushed in."

"Eve" "W-well then... I'll be going now. P-please don't tell anyone about today.{change:Eve,cry}"

"Me" "Don't worry."

"Clara" "Don't worry."

"Eve" "And... Clara."

"Clara" "Mm?"

"Eve" "Next time, please use the door."

"" "Clara seemed to think about it for a full second."

"Clara" "I'll try."

"Eve" "P-please, please use the door.{change:Eve,cry}"

"" "The door closed."

actor exit Eve

# Scene 4-5: The Deduction Club's Finale
