"" "The clubroom fell quiet again."
"" "I looked at the cup of tea on the desk, now half-empty."

"Me" "By the way. That line of reasoning—from 'not in a hidden spot' to finding the disguised letter—it wouldn't have been possible without you either."

"" "Clara tilted her head."

actor show Clara face=neutral at 2
"Clara" "Oh, it wasn't that impressive.{change:Clara,preset:dir_left|face=happy}"

